    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1903-09-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1903-09-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="186"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d186">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Beaupré</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">United States Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-09-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 17, 1903</hi>
                        </date>. (Received 7.30 p.m., 18.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>September 17, 11 a.m. No discussion of canal question and no change in the
                    situation.</p>
                <p>The probability is that Congress will not adjourn before 20th proximo.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Beaupré.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
